<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,998,2030]" pageId="1" pageNumber="53">
Larval variability. The suboccipital bumps sometimes appear to be absent, and the anterolateral thoracic projections, if present, vary in their development. Abdominal terga 
<number box="[943,958,1965,1991]" pageId="1" pageNumber="53" value="3.0">3</number>
and 
<number box="[1015,1030,1965,1991]" pageId="1" pageNumber="53" value="8.0">8</number>
